name: TLF Parts: Desktop design for an e-commerce store
description:
This is a simple design created for TLF Parts, a wholesale that specializes in mobile spare parts and accessories.


Their goal was to present their business values by highlighting the importance of their mission to make diving into GSM business easier for startups, not just already established companies and repair stores.


This file contains mockups, style guide, sitemap, and few prototypes for main menu, buttons, search etc.
